{"tid":493500,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"最愛往往難以相廝守","createTime":"2017-12-08T14:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T05:34:46.000Z","uid":160854,"like":66,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7892ca6c8d1ae29921c9c214c3626aab00730232","tid":493500,"uid":160854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:43:56.000Z","msg":"人愈大愈發現最愛個個往往唔可以一齊一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n終於明點解以前啲人成日話結婚個個唔係最愛 只係最適合<br />\n最遺憾嘅大概係係自己最冇能力嘅年紀 遇到一個最想照顧一世嘅女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地可能一齊經歷過著住對拖鞋落樓下坐下吹下水散下步<br />\n可能經歷過大時大節窮到冇錢買禮物<br />\n可能經歷過父母反對<br />\n你地一一挨過左 但最後都係因為現實 因為幼稚 因為爭拗而分開<br />\n你地會各自過自己既人生<br />\n但總會係某一個特別嘅場地 某一個特別嘅日子<br />\n諗起個個一年只會聯絡一兩次 講聲生日快樂嘅佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796ad75a41db36d034982ae730ff5bcc28177f31","tid":493500,"uid":77729,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:48:20.000Z","msg":"睇完好心up <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74522c33a9db328099c59eea2234ae4393159d5b","tid":493500,"uid":160854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:57:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完好心up <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nI know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee60bc5d6ad094edd20346ac98f70afcd31f8e03","tid":493500,"uid":41602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T15:07:00.000Z","msg":"大概"},{"pid":"ce9d5fbd5828cd4e6c8e0ffd14a2330a3d9e6eb8","tid":493500,"uid":74139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T15:38:56.000Z","msg":"聽日佢生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a3cd6e76161a3b5f62e7e7b4b29359283be3f61","tid":493500,"uid":828,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T15:50:21.000Z","msg":"證明感情總是善良 殘忍的是 人會成長"},{"pid":"2b62c9e6df211f6d19afd3460e2c26b2f980741d","tid":493500,"uid":160854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T16:20:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽日佢生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講句生日快樂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cfb542336c3ee49ea574f51f5918230a82ea081","tid":493500,"uid":162146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T17:06:23.000Z","msg":"分手就不必勉強傷感<br />\n為什麼扯著對方痛著兩難<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bc53aa53b669b0ed60bca863f5229a30dbfa648","tid":493500,"uid":160854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T17:49:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分手就不必勉強傷感<br />\n為什麼扯著對方痛著兩難<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40e64c50e742ee881155778e3d8563dc984d1e28","tid":493500,"uid":151780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T17:53:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"017ff45b8c6ad5613bf5505192c843f0c37fa0a3","tid":493500,"uid":160854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T18:04:44.000Z","msg":"即使到最後留有遺憾 你仍然冇後悔同過佢一齊<br />\n或者留有空白嘅結局對大家黎講都係最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50877c5ec368ada10dd72a67939ffa491a1b0f1b","tid":493500,"uid":18005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T18:07:08.000Z","msg":"唉<br />\n不要再說了"},{"pid":"1ed8b609963eda34dbaafca6d04336f36a6d31cb","tid":493500,"uid":160010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T18:50:46.000Z","msg":"其實有時會諗係因為當時自己冇俾最好既佢 有遺憾所以先咁難忘 定真係有咁愛"},{"pid":"5dc2286da4735a7a2304ab4db64ff363eb0ec74d","tid":493500,"uid":27793,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T19:20:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\">你地可能一齊經歷過著住對拖鞋落樓下坐下吹下水散下步<br />\n可能經歷過大時大節窮到冇錢買禮物<br />\n可能經歷過父母反對<br />\n你地一一挨過左 但最後都係因為現實 因為幼稚 因為爭拗而分開</span><br />\n<br />\n中晒 咁啱一齊個三年都經歷晒呢啲<br />\n同初戀男友<br />\n<br />\n但我無放唔低佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為諗返起佢幼稚到講野點傷害我<br />\n就一啲都唔會掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我成日諗 如果有時光機<br />\n我會直接skip撚左佢<br />\n用盡方法識現任好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e976da881dee3eab184f030c599136825f3ca6","tid":493500,"uid":27793,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T19:24:14.000Z","msg":"好似係台灣書講過：<br />\n若用電腦存檔方式來比喻過去的戀情，<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「 女人是覆寫存檔，男人是另存新檔」。</strong>"},{"pid":"0e36e6fce9d3b7e0de0c945d6d437d02201fb75c","tid":493500,"uid":70695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T20:22:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實有時會諗係因為當時自己冇俾最好既佢 有遺憾所以先咁難忘 定真係有咁愛</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf138629be6035fbf6effebb037a44b35e2bff9","tid":493500,"uid":51343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T20:25:34.000Z","msg":"不能同意更多"},{"pid":"f57be6a9d02dc4bdbffc08967e3921b965c652bb","tid":493500,"uid":719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T22:50:37.000Z","msg":"樓主個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a2dcc8a80d9c786eaddcce211822bf9ad98cc73","tid":493500,"uid":160854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T02:04:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: violet;\">你地可能一齊經歷過著住對拖鞋落樓下坐下吹下水散下步<br />\n可能經歷過大時大節窮到冇錢買禮物<br />\n可能經歷過父母反對<br />\n你地一一挨過左 但最後都係因為現實 因為幼稚 因為爭拗而分開</span><br />\n<br />\n中晒 咁啱一齊個三年都經歷晒呢啲<br />\n同初戀男友<br />\n<br />\n但我無放唔低佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為諗返起佢幼稚到講野點傷害我<br />\n就一啲都唔會掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我成日諗 如果有時光機<br />\n我會直接skip撚左佢<br />\n用盡方法識現任好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但冇當時嘅佢 未必有今日嘅你<br />\n你未必咁識同現任相處呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41499b10d563eda33cfbeeaef03de416100c10ff","tid":493500,"uid":59857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T03:06:38.000Z","msg":"難道我可以扭轉宿命重遇你一次"},{"pid":"9ac76c9e270df07ec744b6040c1f29a812b14078","tid":493500,"uid":59857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T03:06:38.000Z","msg":"難道我可以扭轉宿命重遇你一次"},{"pid":"70928d73c1d98411a04a0a8b9ef8535fa2cea2c3","tid":493500,"uid":160854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T05:34:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>難道我可以扭轉宿命重遇你一次</blockquote><br />\n故事終結早已注定沒法制止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb76325371847d434364bcad1012452975d51a4","tid":493500,"uid":160854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T05:34:46.000Z","msg":"每日最難挨嘅 係訓醒個下同臨訓前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}